Making parts of your image transparent will convert it to PNG if it isn't already.

Advanced settings

Perception, or Delta E, is a metric for understanding how the human eye perceives color difference, where 0 means that the difference between two colors is not perceptible by human eyes and 100 means that the two colors are exact opposites. Chroma Key uses this value to remove colors that look similar to the specified color to produce better results. You can read more here.
